abstract: Retief Goosen takes second-round lead at Northern Trust Open golf tournament in Los Angeles; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: Goosen rolled in a 30-foot birdie putt on his final hole in the Northern Trust Open in Los Angeles to finish in a spot where he had not been in a long time: atop the leaderboard going into the weekend.
